  "description": "## Deep Component Audit тАФ hx-radio-group\n\n**Component directory:** `packages/hx-library/src/components/hx-radio-group/`\n**Sub-components:** hx-radio\n**wc-mcp Health Score:** radio-group=89 (B), radio=95 (A)\n**Known issues:** radio-group: formAssociated, _internals, _groupEl, _hasErrorSlot, _groupId, _helpTextId, _errorId, _handleRadioSelect, _handleKeydown missing. radio: _inputId missing.\n\n### wc-mcp Tools тАФ USE THESE\n- `score_component`, `get_component`, `analyze_accessibility`, `validate_usage`, `list_css_parts`, `list_events`, `list_slots`, `get_design_tokens`\n- **Report wc-mcp bugs to `/Volumes/Development/booked/wc-tools` board.**\n\n### Audit Scope\n1. **Design Tokens** тАФ `--hx-` tokens. Radio circle, checked indicator, label, error. Dark mode.\n2. **Accessibility** тАФ WCAG 2.1 AA. radiogroup role. Radio button ARIA pattern. Arrow key navigation within group. Required. Error.\n3. **Functionality** тАФ Group value. Individual radio values. Form integration. Validation. Horizontal/vertical layout. Error/help text.\n4. **TypeScript** тАФ Strict. formAssociated. ElementInternals. No `any`.\n5. **CSS/Styling** тАФ Shadow DOM. Custom radio indicator. CSS Parts. Layout.\n6. **CEM Accuracy** тАФ Fix all missing descriptions (9 + 1).\n7. **Tests** тАФ 80%+ coverage. Selection. Arrow keys. Form. Validation.\n8. **Storybook** тАФ Vertical/horizontal. Required. Error. Disabled items.\n9. **Drupal Compatibility** тАФ Radios form element. Twig-friendly.\n10. **Portability** тАФ CDN-ready. Form-associated.\n\n### Deliverable\nDetailed audit report. Fix CRITICAL+HIGH. Document rest.",
